Assume our `JSON` payload looks like below:

    {
      &quot;a&quot;: &quot;text&quot;,
      &quot;b&quot;: &quot;35&quot;,
      &quot;c&quot;: {
        &quot;d&quot;: &quot;another&quot;,
        &quot;dd&quot;:3.44E3
      },
      &quot;e&quot;: [
        &quot;array&quot;,
        35,
        2.3E5
      ],
      &quot;f&quot;: 1.1E4,
      &quot;g&quot;: 0.00000000000003
    }

Example code:

